</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0466-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0466-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>Letter not found.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0466-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0466-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>The <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Nancy</span>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0466-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0466-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>John Adams on this date obtained leave from Congress to go home and on the following day began his journey (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ L. H. Butterfield, ed. &lt;i&gt;Diary and Autobiography of John Adams&lt;/i&gt;. 4 vols. Cambridge, Mass., 1961. ]">Butterfield, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Adams Diary and Autobiography</span></span>, 2:22324).</p>

</div>
